{"tid":2095012,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"經典組合Bee Gees開拍音樂傳記片　Rami被看好飾演已故成員Robin","createTime":"2020-07-05T06:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T06:54:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b9675ec87b979b1345f76838469913ffb72368","tid":2095012,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"殿堂級搖滾樂隊Queen傳記電影《波希米亞狂想曲：搖滾傳說》（Bohemian Rhapsody）於2018年上架後大受歡迎，隨即帶起電影公司拍歌手傳記電影的熱潮。早前有消息指將會開拍英國傳奇兄弟組合Bee Gees的音樂傳記，並希望雷米馬利克（Rami Malek）及畢利谷巴（Bradley Cooper）分別飾演已故成員Robin Gibb和Barry Gibb。<br />\n<br />\n據外國傳媒報道，已故成員Robin Gibb的兒子RJ去年開始跟《波希米亞狂想曲：搖滾傳說》監製Graham King籌備拍攝Bee Gees的音樂傳記電影，RJ在訪問中表示Rami Malek是飾演父親的最佳人選：「當我看Rami飾演Freddie Mercury的時候，他令我想起父親跟組合在1976年唱《Massachusetts》的時期。」至於Bee Gees其他成員成員，RJ就很希望Barry Gibb由畢利谷巴（Bradley Cooper）飾演，並已透過公司向對方發出邀請，不過對方暫時還未有任何回覆。<br />\n<br />\nBee Gees由三兄弟Barry Gibb、Robin Gibb和Maurice Gibb組成，自1958年出道便叱吒樂壇幾十載。組合的曲風非常多元化，由流行曲、騷靈，甚至搖滾都有，更憑《Saturday Night Fever》、《Stayin' Alive》、《Night Fever》等經典金曲，帶起了Disco熱潮。很可惜，Maurice和Robin Gibb先後於2003年及2012年相繼病逝，只剩大哥Barry Gibb一人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200705/356401434918522880.jpeg/K-DtYQV1XruptQHWLEP355-TnCVBD6XaiGQzNYhkMzU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200705%2F356401434918522880.jpeg%2FK-DtYQV1XruptQHWLEP355-TnCVBD6XaiGQzNYhkMzU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=bba50261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200705/356411211056812032.jpeg/txk6g74UvlOER-x0LOw7fwKGCKgc0nZx_d0zUP3dM1A?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200705%2F356411211056812032.jpeg%2Ftxk6g74UvlOER-x0LOw7fwKGCKgc0nZx_d0zUP3dM1A%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=05282c22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1d26b45d9588d30a742dba18a63b12b7a27fb07","tid":2095012,"uid":330227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"又係Rami<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係咁似樣咩"},{"pid":"32e7614924aa0111a75489732917bd2b1ffee1fe","tid":2095012,"uid":59699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"mama mia~"},{"pid":"879a86aff8e98aa7d62187e41188d02aa7d62f94","tid":2095012,"uid":59699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"mamma mia~"}]}